interacting with it;

00:16:14.380 --> 00:16:17.910
how they are discovering it,
downloading it, installing it;

00:16:17.910 --> 00:16:21.620
when, under which conditions
they're upgrading to a paid

00:16:21.620 --> 00:16:23.500
